---
description: Naming Conventions
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx,css}
alwaysApply: true
---
Directories/files: kebab-case (e.g., user-profile, feed-page.tsx).

Variables/functions: camelCase, use verbs for booleans (e.g., isLoading, handleSubmit).

Components/types/interfaces: PascalCase.

Event handlers: handleX (e.g., handleLogin).